{"tid":800026,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[比你想像中難嘅數學題] 夾錢搭的士","createTime":"2018-08-30T14:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T23:28:34.000Z","uid":92230,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"230971bc572b9f14a29d924c973ea74c37341624","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"A同B兩個人夾份搭的士.<br />\n直去A嘅目的地要 a 咁多錢<br />\n直去B嘅目的地要 b 咁多錢<br />\nA目的地同B目的地之間要 c 咁多錢<br />\n<br />\n假設:<br />\n1. 的士linear咁收費, 的士constant speed (i.e. 分錢 equivalent to 分距離)<br />\n2. 夾份搭有可能會兜左路, (完全順路係一個special case)<br />\n<br />\n我諗左個答案, 但唔知啱唔啱, 想睇大家討論下, 一陣再拋多啲point出黎. :<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926e2822ecdd48ef8f09d82877cc4fad15367d71","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabf740736f851dad8204d0eeb4b4968aa730730","tid":800026,"uid":192491,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"926e2822ecdd48ef8f09d82877cc4fad15367d71","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"問題呢???????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba13c7bb1aa855b37da9466c987c73c30e02c92","tid":800026,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f152a33608bb77a7d489ab9584bcb6d90b87780","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eabf740736f851dad8204d0eeb4b4968aa730730","tid":800026,"uid":192491,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"926e2822ecdd48ef8f09d82877cc4fad15367d71","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"問題呢???????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"WLOG假設a&lt;b<br />\n咁會揀先去A後去B<br />\n咁而家車費係a+c<br />\n<br />\nA同B各自要俾幾多錢?"},{"pid":"85d53e5564c4f2f94f98393f81d9b04f6febf57f","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"唔順路一齊搭的士預感有一個要抵諗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f517c7692a12d3e9dcb35e8b0aa0dbf3c41abe92","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d53e5564c4f2f94f98393f81d9b04f6febf57f","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"唔順路一齊搭的士預感有一個要抵諗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"預左*"},{"pid":"c4086bd14ef769e0d910c57425e0e2a709cbc41e","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"點解負評, 其實題目已經講明夾錢搭的士, 問題咪就係點夾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb22e27ac80f668dc17dc615a78fa8947fdb2c83","tid":800026,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"A: a/2<br />\nB: b-a/2=c<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 9up"},{"pid":"5aa6945595e0740d33cfa0c92cba2e7977fcc7ea","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f517c7692a12d3e9dcb35e8b0aa0dbf3c41abe92","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d53e5564c4f2f94f98393f81d9b04f6febf57f","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"唔順路一齊搭的士預感有一個要抵諗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"預左*"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"所以其實答案有bound, 太唔公平咁分寧願分開搭,<br />\n可能要諗埋game theory,<br />\n但我只係向左geometry既方向諗已經發覺條問題比我想像中複雜好多.<br />\n<br />\n當p, q分別係A同B最後俾既錢, <br />\n咁必定係<br />\na/2 &lt; p &lt; a<br />\nb/2 &lt; q &lt; b"},{"pid":"42e6adf07315e7288845b33b627856eca507b1c6","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb22e27ac80f668dc17dc615a78fa8947fdb2c83","tid":800026,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"A: a/2<br />\nB: b-a/2=c<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 9up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"呢個係完全順路既special case solution <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一個special case係 a = b = c (等邊三角形, 完全唔順路)<br />\nsolution係A俾a, B俾b (i.e. 最後車資a+c, A同B平分)"},{"pid":"879df166547103a32e850d180eac867ea276a8f5","tid":800026,"uid":19979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"Original = a + b <br />\nprofit (if any) = a + b - (a + c) = b - c<br />\nA &amp; B share the profit"},{"pid":"a2e0e6e6b7777308eecf6a5e08a7d15a2cf6289b","tid":800026,"uid":22302,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"有咩條件先<br />\n你完全冇比條件咁佢兩個鐘意點夾錢都得架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72effc38088ef15ebb296f784af5678c3f2a6873","tid":800026,"uid":72465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過照講如果係我我會點分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假設唔計 B 兜遠咗路嘅 time cost<br />\n先估算最後車資 = a + c<br />\n最後車資按 a b 嘅比例分攤<br />\ni.e.<br />\nA 要比 a(a + c) / (a + b)<br />\nB 要比 b(a + c) / (a + b)"},{"pid":"9481f851769522d16a3a54bae02b1f91fc1b924e","tid":800026,"uid":72465,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5aa6945595e0740d33cfa0c92cba2e7977fcc7ea","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f517c7692a12d3e9dcb35e8b0aa0dbf3c41abe92","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d53e5564c4f2f94f98393f81d9b04f6febf57f","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"唔順路一齊搭的士預感有一個要抵諗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"預左*"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"所以其實答案有bound, 太唔公平咁分寧願分開搭,<br />\n可能要諗埋game theory,<br />\n但我只係向左geometry既方向諗已經發覺條問題比我想像中複雜好多.<br />\n<br />\n當p, q分別係A同B最後俾既錢, <br />\n咁必定係<br />\na/2 &lt; p &lt; a<br />\nb/2 &lt; q &lt; b"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"Game theory 就冇話公唔公平嘅<br />\n兩個都想自己比少 D，最後兩個都 GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd45e69b005387c2f7924097d40fbc37cbce410f","tid":800026,"uid":41975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:50:25.000Z","msg":"坐車頭果個比哂"},{"pid":"2ae3756e300fc39c2c71a7a9e5693095c4b99166","tid":800026,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"首先，如果用game theory黎霖，假設本身就知道a,b,c三個價錢<br />\n1.因為全程要平過自己搭佢地先願意夾份搭<br />\n所以，c&lt;a |c&lt;b<br />\n2.如果 c&lt;a,所以會揀先去b再去a,全程車費b+c。<br />\n如果想公平，去b個人應該俾b-(a-c)/2,去a個人應該俾c+(a-c)/2<br />\n3.如果c&lt;b,就反轉頭先個例子。<br />\n4.如果c&lt;a&lt;b，係鬼都知應該揀先去a再去b,logic同2,3一樣<br />\n利申認真撚"},{"pid":"67e696182999850c87d9140300e26d52a96d3a72","tid":800026,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9481f851769522d16a3a54bae02b1f91fc1b924e","tid":800026,"uid":72465,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5aa6945595e0740d33cfa0c92cba2e7977fcc7ea","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f517c7692a12d3e9dcb35e8b0aa0dbf3c41abe92","tid":800026,"uid":171523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"預左*"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"所以其實答案有bound, 太唔公平咁分寧願分開搭,<br />\n可能要諗埋game theory,<br />\n但我只係向左geometry既方向諗已經發覺條問題比我想像中複雜好多.<br />\n<br />\n當p, q分別係A同B最後俾既錢, <br />\n咁必定係<br />\na/2 &lt; p &lt; a<br />\nb/2 &lt; q &lt; b"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"Game theory 就冇話公唔公平嘅<br />\n兩個都想自己比少 D，最後兩個都 GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"未必"},{"pid":"9517aacfdd3be2467eb71a3b9322e1fdc3e153be","tid":800026,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e185f9046fa3a83ca6e9f2cb1c89f77376e2e927","tid":800026,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae3756e300fc39c2c71a7a9e5693095c4b99166","tid":800026,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"首先，如果用game theory黎霖，假設本身就知道a,b,c三個價錢<br />\n1.因為全程要平過自己搭佢地先願意夾份搭<br />\n所以，c&lt;a |c&lt;b<br />\n2.如果 c&lt;a,所以會揀先去b再去a,全程車費b+c。<br />\n如果想公平，去b個人應該俾b-(a-c)/2,去a個人應該俾c+(a-c)/2<br />\n3.如果c&lt;b,就反轉頭先個例子。<br />\n4.如果c&lt;a&lt;b，係鬼都知應該揀先去a再去b,logic同2,3一樣<br />\n利申認真撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"因為全程要平過自己搭佢地先願意夾份搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290485395c43cbebfcf015f9120380e4881f4b88","tid":800026,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"一定要再加assumption, 身在MK, 一個去柴灣, 一個去荃灣, 唔通搭同一架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348f6820e9d29ffa529ca3ce201e5a6a8df55252","tid":800026,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"要交更呀巴打，下架啦"},{"pid":"7384044d068ab4560870c766290ec3059dcd0a11","tid":800026,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得最公平的方法就係「兩個人省到的百分比相同」。<br />\n<br />\n假設車費係$10/km<br />\n例如下面依幅圖咁，如果兩個人各自搭的士返屋企，總車費就係$90。<br />\n但如果先去A再去B，總車費就係$70，即係兩個人加埋節省到$20。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/230610_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F230610_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=f323cb1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我的條件係「兩個人省到的百分比相同」<br />\n假設A節省到的錢係a，而B節省到的錢係b，兩個人節省到錢佔分開搭的百分比要相同：<br />\na/40 = (20-a)/50<br />\n50a = 800-40a<br />\n90a = 800<br />\na = 80/9<br />\n<br />\n即係A節省到80/9，B節省到20-80/9 = 100/9。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，A需要付$40 - 80/9 = 280/9<br />\nB需要付$50 - 100/9 = 350/9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/230712_3240826d969d2ea1dd91cf1a1f25aabb.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F230712_3240826d969d2ea1dd91cf1a1f25aabb.PNG&h=b0dbab18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ee122c3980194614dc881568c94558419d99d5b","tid":800026,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7384044d068ab4560870c766290ec3059dcd0a11","tid":800026,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得最公平的方法就係「兩個人省到的百分比相同」。<br />\n<br />\n假設車費係$10/km<br />\n例如下面依幅圖咁，如果兩個人各自搭的士返屋企，總車費就係$90。<br />\n但如果先去A再去B，總車費就係$70，即係兩個人加埋節省到$20。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/230610_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F230610_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=f323cb1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我的條件係「兩個人省到的百分比相同」<br />\n假設A節省到的錢係a，而B節省到的錢係b，兩個人節省到錢佔分開搭的百分比要相同：<br />\na/40 = (20-a)/50<br />\n50a = 800-40a<br />\n90a = 800<br />\na = 80/9<br />\n<br />\n即係A節省到80/9，B節省到20-80/9 = 100/9。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，A需要付$40 - 80/9 = 280/9<br />\nB需要付$50 - 100/9 = 350/9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/230712_3240826d969d2ea1dd91cf1a1f25aabb.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F230712_3240826d969d2ea1dd91cf1a1f25aabb.PNG&h=b0dbab18&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"呢個係咪 = #14"},{"pid":"0dd1bddbe243e1b2563a00629b77462c0dc32343","tid":800026,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個係咪 = #14</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n兩個的諗法相同<br />\n至於根據依個條件咩情況下夾得成，咩情況下夾唔成就係geometry問題"}]}